Name: Enrolled last 7-days
Description: The total during the past 7 days, based on your portal's time zone.

Name: All team IDs
Description: The team IDs of all default and custom owner properties for this record.

Name: Campaigns
Description: Campaigns that list this workflow as an asset.

Name: Contact object's trigger
Description: Only applicable to older workflows with the "Contact" object type.
Options: Contact date property (PROPERTY_ANCHOR); Fixed date (STATIC_ANCHOR); Standard (STANDARD)

Name: Metrics Status
Description: Flag indicating flow is enabled for conversion reporting

Name: Object create date/time
Description: The date and time at which this object was created. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Current Issue Count
Description: Number of active issues on a given Automation Platform Flow

Name: Current issues
Description: Issues that haven't been reviewed yet.

Name: Deleted By
Description: User that deleted the workflow

Name: On or Off
Description: "On" means that any enrollees will proceed through the workflow's actions.

Name: Trigger Type
Options: -- (NEW); Events (EVENT); Filter criteria (LIST); Dataset (DATASET); External Data Source (EXTERNAL_DATA_SOURCE); Unified Trigger (UNIFIED_TRIGGER)

Name: Flow ID
Description: ID of the platform flow

Name: Folder
Description: Name of the containing folder

Name: Deleted
Description: Is the flow deleted

Name: Used by other tools
Description: If yes, the tools that use this workflow are shown in the workflow's "connections" panel.

Name: Last action on
Description: The last time that any action effected any enrollee in the workflow.

Name: Last issue occurred on
Description: Workflows can have multiple issues. This is the last occurrence of the most recent issue.

Name: Last issue occurred
Description: Date and time of most recent issue activation on this flow

Name: Object last modified date/time
Description: Most recent timestamp of any property update for this object. This includes HubSpot internal properties, which can be visible or hidden. This property is updated automatically.

Name: May use credits
Description: Does the workflow potentially use credits when run

Name: Record ID
Description: The unique ID for this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Record source detail 1
Description: First level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source detail 2
Description: Second level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source detail 3
Description: Third level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source
Description: How this record was created.

Name: Object type
Description: The object type that can be enrolled in this workflow.

Name: Is re-enrollment enabled
Description: Is the workflow re-enrolling objects

Name: Created in
Description: The HubSpot app where the workflow was created.

Name: Enrolled total
Description: The total number of times the workflow has started, including re-enrollments.

Name: Total lifetime issue activation count
Description: This is the total number of times that an issue has been activated on a flow

Name: Enrolled unique
Description: An estimate of how many different records have enrolled in the workflow.
